{"type": "article", "id": 23448, "title": "旋转衣架", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-08T07:30:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 29, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607141233yRerikAuXCHKp3sE.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是一个可旋转的衣架，由危地马拉设计师 Luis Arrivillaga 为意大利品牌 Living Divani 设计。沿着中轴可以依次打开四个小框，以任意一个点做支撑，由高到低，有简单几何图形感。开合方便也有助于适应不同形状的墙面并将它收到墙边。衣架由橡木制作，有原色或黑色。<a href=\"http://arrivillagabasile.com/\">有兴趣可以点击工作室链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide medium-insert-active\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607141232tsXa31whQMOmSCy9.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70571429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607141232RqcigVsG9yX2PA3v.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.86969253\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607141232Q02Cap1DHU3VENsw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.24450952\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607141233WUp5NYJQe3yTXIi2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.24\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}